div.font: Hi, I'm Max! I'm a software developer with two years of industry experience developing full-stack application and managing cloud infrastructure.

font.font: My journey in programming began at the age of 14 when I wrote my first website. Since then, my passion for technology has only grown. This led me to
font.span: pursue a degree in Computer Science at the University of Nottingham, where I continue to improve my skills as a software developer.

div.font: In my free time, I enjoy reading tech books and articles, exploring open-source code, and building random projects. Outside of tech, I love socialising, visiting museums and historical landmarks, and exploring restaurants in London with my partner.
